      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-05-06T08:45:40.7574690Z",
      "original_text": "\"So, it fears fire? Don't you have incendiary weapons?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-06T08:45:40.7574700Z",
          "locale_text": "\"Yani ateşten mi korkuyor? Elinizde yakıcı silahlar var mı?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«¿Teme el fuego, entonces? ¿Acaso no tienen armas incendiarias?».",
